{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"大字报小诗","authors":["袁水拍　华君武"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":11,"day":21}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大字报小诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是资产阶级立场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为富裕中农帮腔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和帝国主义者合唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身在曹营心在汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矛头指向党！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右倾机会主义分子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪恶昭彰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小毛病他挑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没毛病他剔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动不动否定一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要兴高采烈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右倾的病历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——千篇一律。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风往这边吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腰往这边摆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草往那边动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腿往那边弯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个“主义”指挥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——右倾机会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所见何其小！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所知何其少！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偏偏自命独到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个也不行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个也不好……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是自大狂者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知地厚天高；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是阶级本能作怪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快改造！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不磨生锈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不洗要脏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不烧不成铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不炼怎成钢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有错就改，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向人民还账。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跌倒了，爬起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回头是——党！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那岸渡到这岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧掉来时船！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投进集体无保留，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心广天地宽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七看得深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想得广，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锐利如电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和煦如春阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚定如磐石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"智慧比海洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为劳动群众操心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为子孙万代着想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的心灵啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是党！\t袁水拍诗　华君武画（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}